{"tid":1351571,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"預測香港嘅未來「塔羅」","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T04:05:41.000Z","uid":87680,"like":394,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbde7e2c0379b120de60c5b3048efda0988e88d","tid":1351571,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"我朋友用時間之流牌陣為香港既未來占卜，而我幫手分析，各位塔羅師可以一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錯請指證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b96tuZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb96tuZP.png&h=d2a9d4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「左至右 1至3號位置」<br />\n一號位置代表過去：魔法師（逆）<br />\n解釋：過去既香港因爲一個人嘅決定引致失去控制、到達無法控制局面。（人像向下倒轉⋯我諗大家知咩意思⋯）<br />\n二號位置代表現在：星星（逆）<br />\n解釋：現在只剩下絕望與沮喪。<br />\n三號位置代表未來：太陽（正）<br />\n解釋：未來將會成功，同獲取自由。<br />\n總結及建議：黎明到來之前係最黑暗，只要渡過黑暗太陽就會升起，塔羅已經展示左香港嘅未來，一定會成功！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS：覺得迷惘既人可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b1aebaaa5cfcab5754a72e76798b53f3805364","tid":1351571,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"951780786f2f03f51465550d25ce3d154ec5ff4c","tid":1351571,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b515a32ea7d9bc4e8b98b2f8398cf43feb37c45","tid":1351571,"uid":231124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1351394/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1351394/page/1</a><br />\n[長期置頂/集思廣益]727 元朗地勢分析/討論<br />\n入黎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6aad7b8531d147e530cce1a333e4a688870daea","tid":1351571,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim