9","tid":1351571,"uid":140492,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"未來係幾時 係有大家決定"},{"pid":"2c445efa7584ca0d931ff004c8369ae069c22497","tid":1351571,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"多謝鼓勵"},{"pid":"e5350cc2e6738389cc047738d3d2601e9db14a31","tid":1351571,"uid":176116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f924d16d3069d962d503e5734ee2f9cbdc96d3d6","tid":1351571,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"希望係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170005090d26b5bf81d1447597ec44f86b7a6322","tid":1351571,"uid":269044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:06:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ad54c130c3af6b675ba95cf4dfa565456dd5fa36","tid":1351571,"uid":8659,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"雖然唔主張咁樣去占<br />\n但依牌都講講意見<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎過份既壓抑<br />\n難以伸張自己既主見<br />\n好多野冇辦法順利咁表達出黎<br />\n直至現在依然拘泥於過去既包袱同框架之中<br />\n難以單純地同抱有希望地去面對當下既局面<br />\n當真正能夠心無旁騖<br />\n單純地發乎內心地去做應做之事<br />\n抱有正面既信念<br />\n就會得到光明既結果<br />\n<br />\n寄語<br />\n唔好埋沒自己既想法<br />\n唔好再停留舊有既框架<br />\n發乎內心純乎自然咁去做就得<br />\n勿忘初心"},{"pid":"4e8f0ba94d85293aeb19cac773896646e086290c","tid":1351571,"uid":61517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:03:40.000Z","msg":"多謝代占<br />\n見到太陽呢張牌真係張感覺好好<br />\n所有黑暗事物都會被照耀出黎<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係塔羅師"},{"pid":"7a40587c9beaf217354d55c8cb8877036c653b8c","tid":1351571,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:47:36.000Z","msg":"當香港政府最黑暗野爆光就得 我會咁解"},{"pid":"284f3bfaa67fc6c759c29c02d948eee13150a216","tid":1351571,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:48:58.0