379b120de60c5b3048efda0988e88d","tid":1351571,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"我朋友用時間之流牌陣為香港既未來占卜，而我幫手分析，各位塔羅師可以一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錯請指證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b96tuZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb96tuZP.png&h=d2a9d4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「左至右 1至3號位置」<br />\n一號位置代表過去：魔法師（逆）<br />\n解釋：過去既香港因爲一個人嘅決定引致失去控制、到達無法控制局面。（人像向下倒轉⋯我諗大家知咩意思⋯）<br />\n二號位置代表現在：星星（逆）<br />\n解釋：現在只剩下絕望與沮喪。<br />\n三號位置代表未來：太陽（正）<br />\n解釋：未來將會成功，同獲取自由。<br />\n總結及建議：黎明到來之前係最黑暗，只要渡過黑暗太陽就會升起，塔羅已經展示左香港嘅未來，一定會成功！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS：覺得迷惘既人可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以睇埋支那? 想睇下會唔會支爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58c1b7ef6f322670dec227b281ce90fac647d94","tid":1351571,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"雖然唔信呢d<br />\n但希望你中"},{"pid":"e9edb905e7864884268b31ee2cae2b078c1cebcd","tid":1351571,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"巴打點學塔羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想學"},{"pid":"b5d9d250725912b6645893d51dd888ceeea3b3c6","tid":1351571,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9edb905e7864884268b31ee2cae2b078c1cebcd","tid":1351571,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"巴打點學塔羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"睇書"},{"pid":"5b05208264783973cd18e8825e3054eba3457510","tid":1351571,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":