al/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錯請指證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b96tuZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb96tuZP.png&h=d2a9d4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「左至右 1至3號位置」<br />\n一號位置代表過去：魔法師（逆）<br />\n解釋：過去既香港因爲一個人嘅決定引致失去控制、到達無法控制局面。（人像向下倒轉⋯我諗大家知咩意思⋯）<br />\n二號位置代表現在：星星（逆）<br />\n解釋：現在只剩下絕望與沮喪。<br />\n三號位置代表未來：太陽（正）<br />\n解釋：未來將會成功，同獲取自由。<br />\n總結及建議：黎明到來之前係最黑暗，只要渡過黑暗太陽就會升起，塔羅已經展示左香港嘅未來，一定會成功！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS：覺得迷惘既人可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"成功之前，絕對不可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7b91e0c03af8c67230c42cabe18e1b88972ab9","tid":1351571,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"推背圖43其實都差唔多意思"},{"pid":"db9be79a890db059129017e6dfddea25657e83c8","tid":1351571,"uid":230621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人加油！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"102d7703c4cc14f997e65c91850f84069a66e0b1","tid":1351571,"uid":124914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"推！約定煲底相見"},{"pid":"e6e287a0337f8ae8790237090dfba413d4657f89","tid":1351571,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e023dd7acfbf3320edec78f3632af90bcca615a9","tid":1351571,"uid":24854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e60d4035ae2e0ff7ce6dbbc976262781190986ec","tid":1351571,"uid":8659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04fd6bb58cbbec37f720a7be9546852e98c1b069","tid":1351571,"uid":24854,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"cit